     <section class="privacy-policy">
          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p><small><em>Last Updated: April 14, 2025</em></small></p>

    
          <p>Welcome to ChillPick ("we," "our," or "us"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our entertainment recommendation service.</p>
    
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email, username, and password when you register.</li>
            <li><strong>Activity Data:</strong> Movies/books you add to your watchlist, ratings, and reviews.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and device information for analytics.</li>
          </ul>
    
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide personalized recommendations.</li>
            <li>Improve our service and fix bugs.</li>
            <li>Send account-related emails (e.g., password reset).</li>
            <li>Analyze trends to enhance user experience.</li>
          </ul>
    
          <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your data. We may share it only in these cases:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Trusted third parties (e.g., hosting, analytics) who assist us.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> If required by law (e.g., court orders).</li>
          </ul>
    
          <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use cookies to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Keep you logged in.</li>
            <li>Remember preferences (e.g., dark mode).</li>
            <li>Track site usage via Google Analytics.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
    
          <h2>5. Security</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Password encryption (bcrypt).</li>
            <li>Secure servers (HTTPS).</li>
            <li>Regular security audits.</li>
          </ul>
    
          <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Access/Delete Data:</strong> Request a copy of your data or delete your account.</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from emails.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@chillpick.com">privacy@chillpick.com</a> for requests.</p>
    
          <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy. Check this page for the latest version.</p>
    
          <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>For questions, email <a href="mailto:contact@chillpick.com">contact@chillpick.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

